[I] Composable command line interface toolkit

[T] Click is a Python package for creating beautiful command line interfaces in
[T] a composable way with as little code as necessary. It's the "Command Line
[T] Interface Creation Kit". It's highly configurable but comes with sensible
[T] defaults out of the box.

[U] https://click.palletsprojects.com/en/stable/

